dogs.name: Zach
dogs.meet: This big goofy guys name is Zach. He is a big sweet pitty mix weighing in at 62 pounds. He is still a young so he still has some growing to do. He loves going on walks and hikes, and during the summer loves the water.

dogs.name: Brinley
dogs.meet: Hi everyone! Brinley here with an important announcement...I'm available for adoption! I'm an 11 week old shepherd/aussie mix and my foster family says I'm cute as a button with the sweetest personality. I'm a super, lovable girl with the best puppy dog eyes that are guaranteed to melt your heart.

dogs.name: Mackenzie
dogs.meet: Meet Mackenzie! This tiny sparkplug is full of puppy energy and love. Her favorite things include: playing with other dogs, trying to play with cats, looking super cute in photos and taking naps. Mackenzie also loves her toys and cuddling.

dogs.name: Goblin
dogs.meet: Meet Goblin! Don't let her name fool you, she's super sweet and cuddly. Her favorite place is on a lap or the heat vent. This girl is not a fan of the cold, but looks adorable in a sweater! With those floppy ears and winning personality she is sure to melt everyone's heart.

dogs.name: Clara Bean
dogs.meet: Meet Clara Bean!! This 8 ish month old pocket pit is so adorable!!! She's tiny with a big personality!! Clara Bean is deaf but that doesn't slow her down a bit! She is learning hand signals for her commands! Clara Bean loves other dogs & loves to play!!
